Install Django: pip3 install Django
Install Python: sudo apt-get install python3 python3-pip
Install "nodejs-legacy" package: apt-get install nodejs-legacy
Install Psycopg2: (pip install psycopg2-binary) (pip install psycopg2==2.7.4) (sudo apt-get install python-psycopg2)
Install UFW: sudo apt-get install ufw
Enable UFW: sudo ufw enable
Remove UFW: sudo apt-get remove ufw

Create a Django Project: Django-admin startproject mysite
Create an app: Python manage.py startapp myapp

Verify Django Version: (python -m django --version) or (django-admin --version) or (pip freeze)
Verify Python Version: python -V
Verify Apache Version: apachectl -V
Verify MySQL Version: MySQL -V
Verify VirtualEnv Version: virtualenv --version
Verify Node.js’s JS Version: node -p process.versions.v8
Verify Node.js Version: Node -v or node --version
Verify Psycopg2 Version: (pip freeze | grep psycopg2) (python -c "import psycopg2; print(psycopg2.__version__)")
Verify UFW Status: sudo ufw status - sudo dpkg --get-selections | grep ufw

Update the system to the latest version: Sudo apt-get update == sudo apt-get dist-upgarde
Update Python: Apt-get install python3.5
Update Django: Sudo pip3 install django --upgrade --install-option-”--prefix-opt/bitnami/apps/django”

Access the Project Folder: cd /opt/bitnami/apps/django/django_projects/Project
Create a Super Admin account: python3 manage.py createsuperuser

Restart Apache: sudo /opt/bitnami/stlscript.sh restart apache

Bitnami destination: opt/bitnami/
